msgstr "手动涡轮激光炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual lacerator"
msgstr "手动撕裂者"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual RM451 flamethrower"
msgstr "手动RM451火焰喷射器"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual perforator"
msgstr "手动穿孔器"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual needler"
msgstr "手动针刺枪"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual hypervelocity driver"
msgstr "手动超高速驱动器"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual ripper"
msgstr "手动撕裂者"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual rotary speargun"
msgstr "手动旋转鱼叉枪"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual scorpion ballista"
msgstr "手动蝎弩"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual splintergun"
msgstr "手动碎片枪"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual speargun"
msgstr "手动鱼叉枪"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual tesla cannon"
msgstr "手动特斯拉炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual avalanche rifle"
msgstr "手动雪崩步枪"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gelatinous capsule"
msgid_plural "gelatinous capsules"
msgstr[0] "凝胶胶囊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gelatinous capsule'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray cocoon'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'oozing pod'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gelatinous capsule', 'str_pl': 'gelatinous
#. capsules'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray cocoon', 'str_pl': 'gray cocoons'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'oozing pod', 'str_pl': 'oozing pods'}
#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid ""
"While the blob is very eager to be fed, it's not as enthusiastic about "
"giving up liquids.  A few alterations are necessary."
msgstr "虽然这团粘液非常渴望被喂食，但它对释放液体就没那么积极了。需要做一些调整。"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gelatinous tank"
msgid_plural "gelatinous tanks"
msgstr[0] "凝胶罐"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gray cocoon"
msgid_plural "gray cocoons"
msgstr[0] "灰色茧"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gray tank"
msgid_plural "gray tanks"
msgstr[0] "灰色罐"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "oozing pod"
msgid_plural "oozing pods"
msgstr[0] "渗流荚"

#: .\items\tools\blob_container.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "oozing tank"
msgid_plural "oozing tanks"
msgstr[0] "渗流罐"

#: .\items\tools\blob_tools.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "growing blob frame"
msgid_plural "growing blob frames"
msgstr[0] "生长中的粘液框架"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'growing blob frame'}.
#: .\items\tools\blob_tools.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid ""
"You test the frame; It wiggles, and then collapses into an lump of goo."
msgstr "你测试了框架；它扭动了一下，然后塌陷成一团粘液。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'growing blob frame'}.
#: .\items\tools\blob_tools.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "You test the frame; it gives easily, it's still not sturdy enough"
msgstr "你测试了框架；它轻易地变形了，仍然不够坚固。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'growing blob frame'}
#: .\items\tools\blob_tools.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid ""
"A growing vehicle frame made of bone.  It's coated in a thick layer of ooze,"
" though there's greater amounts on the bindings.  It's not quite tough "
"enough to use."
msgstr "一个由骨头制成的生长中的载具框架。它覆盖着一层厚厚的粘液，尽管在绑带处更多。它还不够坚韧，无法使用。"

