msgstr "一团粘液分裂并弹开了！"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'multiplying gelatinous mass'}
#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'multiplying gray mass'}
#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'multiplying oozing mass'}
