#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rubber treads'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel treads'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tank treads'}
#: .\vehicleparts\blaze_other_parts.json
msgid ""
"A section of continuous track, the kind mounted on construction vehicles and"
" military fighting vehicles.  It acts as a wheel, and the broad surface "
"provides plenty of traction to move heavy vehicles off-road, but at the cost"
" of speed due to the heavy weight."
msgstr ""
"一段连续履带，安装在工程车辆和军用战斗车辆上的那种。它起到车轮的作用，宽阔的表面提供了充足的牵引力，使重型车辆能够越野行驶，但由于重量大，会牺牲速度。"

